CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 27, 1969, page 1 reads: " Kris and Noel- The first Christmas for Kris and Noel White, three month old twin daughters of Mr. and Mrs. Gerald James White of Pittsburgh is bound to be merry and full of good cheer. Getting into the spirit of things the two young ladies pose in a Christmas Boxes as they wish everyone a Merry Christmas"--Harris Photo
TitMainTitle: Two little girls, Kris and Noel White, twin daughters of Mr. and Mrs. Gerald James White, wearing matching dresses seated in gift-wrapped box, with woman's arm supporting them
